Package: nitty
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libgtk-4-1 (>= 4.6), libssh2-1 (>= 1.10), libc6 (>= 2.35)
Description: Feature-rich terminal emulator written in Nitpick
 Nitty is a terminal emulator built from the ground up for power users.
 It combines standard local shell capabilities with advanced features like
 integrated SSH connection management, a built-in encrypted credential vault,
 SFTP browsing, native serial port and telnet support, and a flexible plugin system.
